		<part id="conclusions">
			<title>Conclusions</title>
			<slide id="api-journey">
				<title>The API Journey</title>
				<ul>
					<li>APIs are necessary for digital transformation</li>
					<li>API value needs <em>APIs</em> and it needs <em>valuable APIs</em></li>
					<li>Getting started is both hard and easy a the same time</li>
					<ul>
						<li><em>Using APIs</em> will not in itself create the desired value</li>
						<li><em>Doing the right thing with APIs</em> requires focus and execution</li>
					</ul>
				</ul>
			</slide>
